HEADWORD: Kitten
<hw>Kit"ten</hw> <pr>(k⟦icr⟧t"t'n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>kiton</ets>, a dim. of <ets>cat</ets>; cf. G. <ets>kitze</ets> a
young cat, also a female cat, and F. <ets>chaton</ets>, dim. of
<ets>chat</ets> cat, also E. <ets>kitling</ets>. See
<er>Cat</er>.]</ety> <def>A young cat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kitten</ent>⟦br⟧

